":"<blockquote>好有呃保險GA氣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鄉下地方保你老母咩保險狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"人地講緊許冠文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/224719_657b076d68ce9a8c771e7a90f2a5ba41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F224719_657b076d68ce9a8c771e7a90f2a5ba41.png&h=c98991f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8a164b3728433f0ce984c405e594faa0a5a714d","tid":506432,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T14:49:50.000Z","msg":"入左結界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/surprise_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c32706e6bae9c46dd68a9cb082edccd09839ab","tid":506432,"uid":742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:17:46.000Z","msg":"應該係訓緊教個陣比人劃花左塊面"},{"pid":"bef8faeead696dc57b29d6ed6d52555b53aba6c1","tid":506432,"uid":713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171222/640_7d10ddf3fbb18836385699c5e4ee9489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171222%2F640_7d10ddf3fbb18836385699c5e4ee9489.jpg&h=5707e4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國一名男子半年前被宣佈死亡兼火化，惟他本人卻懵然不知。這件聽來自相矛盾的事件，發生在44歲的沙功（Sakorn Sachiwa）身上。<br />\n<br />\n遠赴他府工作近兩年的沙功，周日返回東北部四色菊府老家，家人驚多於喜，因為他們都認為沙功已化灰，心想回來的是鬼魂嗎。<br />\n沙功的家人5月接到噩耗，曼谷警局說沙功因血液感染死亡，叫他們到曼谷領回遺體。他們認屍時，見到遺體的門牙齊全，一度質疑他是否「崩牙」的沙功，警方則說跟身份證辦事。家屬也沒有追究下去，將遺體火化，不料事隔半年沙功「回魂」。<br />\n沙功說自己根本沒有死，但遺失身份證卻是真的，之後也沒有聯絡鄉下親人，結果連自己「死」了也不知。他說，2016年初到南部洛坤府（Nakhon Thammarat）一艘漁船工作，其間一名緬甸工人偷了他的身份證後不知所終。<br />\n沙功說，媽媽見到他「返來了」，問他：「你已死了，如何回來？」<span style=\"color: red;\">他聽到媽媽說自己已死，一時渾身無力</span>。他的姐夫說，家人和親戚一直在撫摸他，直到確信他不是鬼為止。家人之後帶他見村中長老，要求他們做公證人，確定沙功身份是如假包換。<br />\n當局正為沙功辦理證件，幫他「還陽」，料需時數周。<br />\n至於被火化的人到底是誰，警方表示會重新調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171222/57612202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612202&d=c9o%2Bp0wmVt%2Bykjwp0NVuhzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=cf90b727\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612202&h=7b015314\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171222/57612202</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己懷疑自己死左？</blockquote><br />\n賣菜婆: 人無心即死<br />\n比干: <span style=\"color: red;\">嗚呀</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"0da265664cd06c042ef9d83c5e1783136d9c8fa6","tid":506432,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"第10集 - 歸去來兮<br />\n<br />\n　　青年男女齊齊玩碟仙，玩得投入之際，突然門鐘一響，原來是剛從外地回來的大偉，大偉看見眾人玩碟仙，大說荒謬。翌日，大夥兒往深山探險，蔡在途中弄亂一堆骷髏骨，戲言女鬼一定漂亮。自此，怪事頻生，大偉更不時看見一女子在他身邊出沒，原來是被他弄亂骷髏骨的女鬼。大偉竟被嚇死了，但原來，那女鬼是假鬼，她是阿華們的朋友，故意佈局嚇大偉的。真正已死的是大偉，他在美國被燒死了，因為阿華們玩碟仙，把他請了回來。"},{"pid":"bd1d30690eb47e89b3e6ff191ef25daced42c843","tid":506432,"uid":6937,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"家人和親戚一直在撫摸他，直到確信他不是鬼為止。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43f923c24b06d52f7a954d21c0ccba3f5f1cdc7","tid":506432,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"驚多於喜 咁佢家人都好愛佢"},{"pid":"6c9b9a56ef4cb76529a9c54d10272e3a14a05d94","tid":506432,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171222/640_7d10ddf3fbb18836385